# HIROSHI DAY 1

label hiro_D1_A:

    "I'm awoken by the sound of shuffling feet outside of my bedroom. 
    In a panicked daze, I stand up and grab one of the bats on my floor."
    
    "I groan in disdain when I see it's my limited edition baby blue Nationally Acclaimed Team SGT signed bat with a minor defect and misprint of the team's name, 
    but I grip it tighter anyway when I hear the sound coming closer."

    "As I tread closer to the door, 
    I shut my eyes and pray to every being out there 
    that I'm not getting mugged at 6 in the morning. 
    And for the strength to actually swing my bat."

    "When I open my door, I'm met by a man looking like he had 
    one too many overtime shifts at a corporate job."

    menu:
        "Choose"
        "Oh my god!":
            jump hiro_D1_AA
        "How did you get in my house?!":
            jump hiro_D1_AB
        "Swing.":
            jump hiro_D1_AC

label hiro_D1_AA:
    "The man is visibly sweating as I yell at him. 
    His eyes widen, and he raises his hands and shoulders to protect himself from my attack. 
    I step back a bit when he does, feeling immediately bad. 
    He covers his face with his hands shakily."

    "???" "S-sorry! I'm sorry, I swear I didn't mean to wake or disturb you or anything! 
    I just… need to get out of here! Please, let me out of here!"

    "At least he seems remorseful. 
    I shake my head in disbelief and scoff, putting my bat down."

    mc "What are you asking permission from me for??? Just go!"

    "He nods furiously and attempts to walk out to my balcony. 
    When he does, I hear a loud poof, and a cloud of smoke covers my vision."

    "What the actual hell?"

    jump hiro_D1_B

label hiro_D1_AB:
    "The man shakes his head in desperation, his gaze fixed to the floor."

    "???" "I really don't know. Look, can I just- can I please get out?"

    "He's fidgeting with his collar. 
    I can see the way he doesn't meet my eyes, and I get impatient."

    mc "Then get out the same way you got in!"

    "He sighs exasperatedly."

    "???" "I don't know how I got in, okay? But this place is just so messy, I can't stand it…"

    "He proceeds to turn and stomps to my balcony. The nerve of this guy!"

    "When I try to chase after him, there's a loud poof, and a cloud of smoke covers my vision. Where is he?"

    jump hiro_D1_B

label hiro_D1_AC:
    "The bat just slightly misses the side of his arm. 
    He dodges, and gets clearly upset, covering his face."

    "???" "What the hell are you doing?!"

    "My mouth is agape when he makes that comment."

    mc "What the hell are YOU doing??? Get the fuck out of my house!"

    "The man scoffs before runs out and attempts to go to my balcony, 
    but I hear a poof, a cloud of smoke appears, and his figure is gone. 
    I drop my bat and walk over to where he had gone. What the hell?"

    jump hiro_D1_B

label hiro_D1_B:
    "I cough when I wave the smoke away to clear the air. 
    I come a little closer to where he had gone, and my foot accidentally kicks an item on the floor."

    mc "Oh… shit."

    "I pick it up, and it's the little figurine I got yesterday from Mystery Sponsor. 
    When I attempt to turn it in my hand, it vibrates and a loud poof is heard along with another cloud of smoke."

    "Goddammit."

    "I cough again and wave my hand to clear the air."

    "The same strange man appears, and he pats himself down frantically. What the hell..?"

    "He turns around and sees me, and his eyes dart across the room we're in."

    "???" "Shit… oh shit…"

    "He gags and shakily falls to his knees. Oh, the drama on this guy!"

    "???" "P-please! Turn me back!"

    "He grasped my hands together, begging me desperately to do whatever 
    had happened to him earlier 
    all while keeping his head down. I furrow my brows."

    mc "Hey. C-calm down!"

    "He shakes my hands more insistently. 
    I can basically feel it get more and more sweaty as he begs."

    "???" "Please! I can't-"

    "He gags again. I let out an offended scoff and shove his hands away. What the fuck is his problem?"

    mc "Look! I-I don't know what to do, alright? I don't know what you want me to do!"

    "???" "Turn me back!"

    "I get even more confused. He stands and backs away, and tries to bow again."

    "???" "L-look, I… I really can't stand looking at the mess inside. It's making me feel so… terribly awful and I just-"

    "He gags again."

    mc "Stop! Just stop, shut up, and calm down!"

    "He shakes his head vehemently, and fidgets with his hands. 
    In a last desperate attempt to calm down, he shuts his eyes. 
    I can see him visibly get calmer when he does."

    "What a prick!"

    "???" "Look… your guess is as good as mine. Sorry… I… I really can't give you a proper answer but..."

    "I try to wrap my head around this strange man. He looks kind of familiar."

    mc "No…"

    "He inhales sharply, clearing his throat."

    "???" "What?"

    menu:
        "Choose"
        "Are you the figurine I got?":
            jump hiro_D1_BA
        "Do you know about Mystery Sponsor?":
            jump hiro_D1_BB
        "Do you remember where you came from?":
            jump hiro_D1_BC

label hiro_D1_BA:
    "The question seemed to make him stop fidgeting and he sighs quietly."

    "???" "I believe s-so…"

    jump hiro_D1_C

label hiro_D1_BB:
    "I see his shoulders slump in defeat when he hears me mention the creature."

    "???" "That th-thing…"

    jump hiro_D1_C

label hiro_D1_BC:
    "He swallows harshly."

    "???" "I-um… remember being… trapped in a box…"

    jump hiro_D1_C

label hiro_D1_C:
    "I rub my face in frustration."

    mc "Okay, okay… So you are the figurine from it…"

    "I can't wrap my head around this ridiculous situation. God forbid a woman gets to open a blind box!"

    "The man fidgets with his collar restlessly, and I get irked."

    mc "Why the hell are you so nervous, anyway? And why the hell were you turned into a collectible by that thing?"

    "He keeps his eyes closed as he answers."

    "???" "The two are completely… unrelated. I'm n-not nervous… I just really, really can't handle- um… extreme messes especially like this. And the creature is… something else entirely…"

    "He slowly goes down to the floor and covers his face."

    "???" "Look, I-I'm sorry I don't really know… I can't really focus right now. How did you even get this house so… God I can smell it from here…"

    "He's now kneeled straight down to the floor with his face buried in his hands. 
    I summon every urge not to yell at this pathetic, shaking man for making me feel levels of 
    shame I never thought I could reach."

    menu:
        "Choose"
        "Shake your head and say how ridiculous he looks right now.":
            jump hiro_D1_CA
        "Pull him up from the floor.":
            jump hiro_D1_CB
        "Tell him he's over-dramatic.":
            jump hiro_D1_CC

label hiro_D1_CA:
    mc "Dude. I know my place is kind of messed up right now, but you're a grown ass man… In corporate clothes nonetheless, shaking on my floor. 
    Really? Get up from there. 
    If you think the inside is dirty, what makes you think the floor out here is cleaner?"

    "The man huffs and groans quietly, rubbing his face in frustration."

    "???" "Alright… okay… I know but… Ugh, no…"

    "He actually stands and finally meets my eyes properly for the first time. 
    My eyes widen when I get a good glimpse of his face."

    "My cheeks heat up."

    jump hiro_D1_D

label hiro_D1_CB:
    "I roll my eyes and kneel to his level."
    
    mc "Hey. Come on. Get up."

    "He shakes his head furiously. Without waiting for anything else, I grab his arm and pull him up gently. 
    I hear him inhale sharply, and he reveals his face when he stands."

    jump hiro_D1_D

label hiro_D1_CC:
    "???" "Me? Over dramatic? Have you seen the state of your own fucking house???"

    "Wow."

    mc "Are you serious right now?! You're the one on the floor crying over a mess that isn't even yours!"

    "I hear him grunt and he stands quietly, and I could finally see his face properly, twisted in disdain."

    jump hiro_D1_D

label hiro_D1_D:
    "When he finally gets a good look at me, I see his eyes flash in recognition. 
    He steps back to give some space between us and coughs to clear his throat."

    "???" "You look young."

    menu:
        "Choose"
        "You look old. Too old to be grovelling on the floor.":
            jump hiro_D1_DA
        "So?":
            jump hiro_D1_DB
        "Roll your eyes.":
            jump hiro_D1_DC


label hiro_D1_DA:
    "He's taken aback, and I see his cheeks flush a bright red."

    "Wow. And he gets flustered easily."

    jump hiro_D1_E

label hiro_D1_DB:
    "He huffs, as if how I replied was beyond him."

    jump hiro_D1_E

label hiro_D1_DC:
    "He shakes his head in disbelief, offended."

    jump hiro_D1_E

label hiro_D1_E:
    "He crosses his arms impatiently, and I see his eyes dart over me once more, observing the state of my house…"
    
    "…and he turns his back on me, shoulders raised."

    "???" "I'm sorry. I-I really can't talk to you in this state…"

    "At this point I'm absolutely fed up by his attitude."
    
    mc "My {i}God{/i} you're fucking insufferable! Fine, then!"

    "I leave him to his whiney drama on the balcony, slamming my bedroom door. 
    I throw myself to my bed and groan frustratingly in my pillow."

    "Now I'm convinced he deserved to get hit by that bat."

